languages.text: «Bien, ¿qué tenemos aquí? Ración doble para ti y tu marido... Pensaba que tu marido había estirado la pata».
languages.original_text: "Right, then, what have we here? Double rations, for you and for your husband... I thought your husband kicked the bucket?"

languages.text: 「あぁ、そうだな、何があったかな？配給が2人分、あんたと旦那の分…旦那は亡くなったんじゃなかったか？」
languages.original_text: "Right, then, what have we here? Double rations, for you and for your husband... I thought your husband kicked the bucket?"

traits.locale_text: 「あぁ、そうだな、何があったかな？配給が2人分、あんたと旦那の分…旦那は亡くなったんじゃなかったか？」

languages.text: "Also, was haben wir hier? Doppelte Rationen für Euch und Euren Gatten ... Ich dachte, Euer Gatte hätte ins Gras gebissen?"
languages.original_text: "Right, then, what have we here? Double rations, for you and for your husband... I thought your husband kicked the bucket?"

languages.text: « Bon, alors, qu'est-ce qu'on a là ? Deux rations, une pour vous, une pour votre mari... Je croyais qu'il était mort, votre mari ? »
languages.original_text: "Right, then, what have we here? Double rations, for you and for your husband... I thought your husband kicked the bucket?"

languages.text: "Pekâlâ, bakalım ne varmış. Kocanla sana çifte kumanya. Senin herif nalları dikmemiş miydi?"
